{"id": "art-153", "label": "Art. 153", "title": "Art. 153: Obţinerea de date privind situaţia financiară a unei persoane", "slug": "art-153", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1502849750\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2379\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1502849750\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153:\nOb&#355;inerea de date privind situa&#355;ia financiar&#259; a unei persoane </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_954482773\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2378\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_954482773\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Procurorul poate solicita unei institu&#355;ii de credit\nsau oric&#259;rei altei institu&#355;ii care de&#355;ine date privind\nsitua&#355;ia financiar&#259; a unei persoane comunicarea datelor privind\nexisten&#355;a &#351;i con&#355;inutul conturilor unei persoane, în cazul în\ncare exist&#259; indicii temeinice cu privire la s&#259;vâr&#351;irea unei\ninfrac&#355;iuni &#351;i exist&#259; temeiuri pentru a se crede c&#259; datele\nsolicitate constituie probe.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1289232800\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2377\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1289232800\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)M&#259;sura prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) se dispune\ndin oficiu sau la cererea organului de cercetare penal&#259;, prin\nordonan&#355;&#259; care trebuie s&#259; cuprind&#259;, în afara\nmen&#355;iunilor prev&#259;zute la art. 286 alin. (2): institu&#355;ia care\neste în posesia ori care are sub control datele, numele suspectului sau\ninculpatului, motivarea îndeplinirii condi&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la alin.\n(1), men&#355;ionarea obliga&#355;iei institu&#355;iei de a comunica imediat,\nîn condi&#355;ii de confiden&#355;ialitate, datele solicitate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_503198246\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2376\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_503198246\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Institu&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) este\nobligat&#259; s&#259; pun&#259; de îndat&#259; la dispozi&#355;ie datele\nsolicitate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL V:Conservarea datelor informatice</span></b></p>"}